{"id":652,"date":"2020-08-13T03:10:00","date_gmt":"2020-08-12T20:10:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?page_id=652"},"modified":"2024-10-21T15:20:02","modified_gmt":"2024-10-21T08:20:02","slug":"saigon-saigon-bar","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/saigon-saigon-bar\/","title":{"rendered":"Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1-1.jpg 1360w, \/?ff_http_action_trigger=1&ff_http_action_name=ff_http_request_resize_and_serve_image&ff_http_action_params%5Bimage% 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/450d81e3e7d189d78ef344df167a6335_Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1-1-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/450d81e3e7d189d78ef344df167a6335_Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1-1-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/450d81e3e7d189d78ef344df167a6335_Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1-1-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Saigon-Saigon-Rooftop-Bar-Header-1360x600-1-1\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47ll6iof fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47ll6iog fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ll6ioj fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/292dcc1668b0bc3045764316883b26b0_Logo-Saigon-Saigon-Bar-1-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar on the 10th floor of Caravelle Saigon\"><div class=\"ffb-id-5crrsjo0 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Savour unlimited fresh air and plenty of stunning views, music nights, and chilling time for you to accompany our refreshing drinks.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Dance the rest night away with live performance:<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* from 21:00 until 24:00 on Mondays, Tuesdays<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Living Cuba Band will deliver your favourite beats:<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* from 21:00 until 24:00 on Wednesdays, Thursdays, Fridays, Saturdays and Sundays.<\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\">Ladies' Night every Wednesday<\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>BUY 1 GET 1<\/strong> for Dark &amp; Stormy, Cuba Libre, White Lady, and Tom Collins.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">And don't miss our <strong>Happy Hour<\/strong> from 17:00 to 19:00 with 50% off for selected drink &ndash; we'll be looking forward to seeing you at Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar!<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4sk0dtsl fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Opening Time:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Mondays to Sundays: 16:00 until late<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">____________________<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">If only these walls could talk. Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar on the top floor of the hotel is one of the few remaining bars in our rapidly-developing city with such a long and colourful history to tell. Way before sky bars, craft beer and social media became &lsquo;things&rsquo;, drinks flowed uninterrupted at Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar from the very first moment the hotel opened way back in 1959. Not even a war could prevent thirsty politicians, journalists and soldiers from risking a sneaky happy hour beer on the patio and balconies that overlook the city and along with one of its most famous and historical streets.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">These days, of course, the risks for guests are nowhere near the same and many things have changed. But one thing that hasn&rsquo;t, is Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar&rsquo;s exceptional service and its special places in the heart of our city where modernity and history continue to collide.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Saigon Saigon Rooftop Bar&rsquo;s new menu has something for everyone. It offers a gentle gateway into Vietnamese cuisine but at the same time offers classic bar food with a twist&hellip;.. And that view!<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4neh38oi buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/SSRB-Master-Drink-List-0524.pdf\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">VIEW MENU<\/span><\/a><\/div><section class=\"ffb-id-82pqksrv fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--2 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-82pqkss0 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-82pqkss2 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssgb-3.jpg\" alt=\"ssgb-3\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-82pqkss3 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-6 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-82pqkss5 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/ssgb-2.jpg\" alt=\"ssgb-2\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-47ll6iof{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-47ll6iog{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-47ll6iof 